          </div>
          <div class="footer-faq-list">
            <div class="faq-accordion">
              <div class="faq-accordion-item">
                <a
                  href=""
                  class="faq-accordion-trigger js-faq-accordion-trigger"
                >
                  <span class="faq-accordion-trigger-text">Which City Is Zahra Ebrahim Based In?</span>
                  <svg class="faq-accordion-trigger-icon">
                    <use href="{{ 'icons.svg' | asset_url }}#symbol-caret"></use>
                  </svg>
                </a>
                <div class="faq-accordion-results js-faq-accordion-results">
                  <div class="faq-accordion-result-content">
                    <p>
                      You Can Visit Our Showroom Within Our Factory. We Are Open Monday To Saturday Between 10 Am And 4
                      Pm. For Directions And Location Please Call On Our Workshop Numbers: 03209000151, 03209000152
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-accordion-item">
